talent level 15 Upgrade Divine Strike
increase agility bonus by 6%
reduce Critical after every hit done by 1

add a new Modifier Weak Point Strike
Every time Daisho crit any enemys, they will suffer from 1 random debuff out of 2 that will only affect Daisho him-self or his spells
DEBUFF 1 Enemys will take 12% more damage from BladeStorm and will have reduce healing by 8%, if Daisho damage them with BladeStorm,
it will have 65% chance to increase the duration of BladeStorm by 0.1 every time they get damage by it. DEBUFF 2 enemys will take 35%
more damage from Wind Walk and if Daisho land a True Strike on them, they will take 70% more damage instead and get stun longer for 0.6
second and bleed for 17 plus 0.2% of their max health in pure damage for 3 seconds. The Weak Point Strike debuff last 4 second and
enemys that got Weak Point Strike cannot get it again for 11 seconds and a Symbol will spawn on their head Showing witch one of the
Debuff they are affected by.

ULTIMATE R TOGGLE Hard Strike and Swift Strike
Daisho can change his mode of attack, In Hard Strike Daisho will increase his base damage, buffing Wind Walk and increasing Divine Strike
Critical damage but reduce his attack speed, losing damage with BladeStorm and for Swift Strike, Reduce Base Attack Time with weapons,
Buffing BladeStorm and also increasing his movement speed but reduce his base damage and Reduce Divine Strike Critical damage

