damage and for Swift Strike, increase daisho Divine Strike critical damage by 10% for every crit done with it while doing auto attack or
BladeStorm that stack up to 20 max and last 2.5 second refresh on hit with auto attack or BladeStorm and if Daisho doesnt attack for 15
he will get 80% increase damage for the next Auto attack when in Hard Strike and for Swift Strike, BladeStorm will have 1.2 second
duration increase and deal 3% increase damage for every -1 armor the enemys lost






